1:16:51.773 --> 1:16:52.774
[bicycle tires rattling]

1:17:05.871 --> 1:17:06.955
We failed him.

1:17:08.540 --> 1:17:09.833
Maybe we all did.

1:17:14.671 --> 1:17:17.758
It was good working with you, KJ Harper.

1:17:21.553 --> 1:17:23.180
Yeah. You too, Fish.

1:17:26.683 --> 1:17:28.310
-See ya around.
-Yep.

